{"tid":1645103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[討論] 全民口罩日常化","createTime":"2019-10-10T18:40:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-25T04:03:31.000Z","uid":15226,"like":29,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"85ad3b263b60b1769a7111a4fd6ba770283cfe0a","tid":1645103,"uid":15226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:40:39.000Z","msg":"唔明點解，有班手足係咁屌人唔參與戴口罩活動<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1644456\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1644456</a><br />\n <br />\n本身係原po留左comment但希望多啲手足睇我既小小意見 所以開一次post<br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論<br />\nBtw希望各位不同意見既手足討論既時候態度可以好小小 平心靜氣 方可以理性討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTo: 正評上面post既手足<br />\n你地到底有冇用個腦黎諗野嫁<br />\n行為藝術 焗 怕被篤灰<br />\n你地係咪搞笑阿 因為呢啲理由而唔帶口罩 間接自我審查 又話逆港共政策而行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n日日帶口罩目的係<br />\n1.對抗惡法 <br />\n2.展現港人決心<br />\n3.抗爭日常化<br />\n<br />\n行為藝術？ <br />\n當初行動po大量正評 大量支持 亦都清晰咁講明係日日帶 點解第日出到黎係咁小人響應？亦都唔係冇人開po講過呢個問題 之後又比人用以上理由話返轉頭 如果呢樣係行為藝術 點解唱歌唔係？求指導<br />\n<br />\n焗？ <br />\n唔係得你一個覺得焗 重點在於大家既決心同自覺性<br />\n<br />\n怕被公司同事篤灰？ <br />\n你到底怕咩 和理非手足其實更加應該積極參與 帶口罩完全冇任何違法 如果藍絲同事要篤既 一早就搵齊料篤你喇 仲等4個月拖咁耐咩 而且一早提醒過大家發夢唔好再po出黎比料人 換言之即係留證據比狗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日常生活夠多人夠回響既時候 唔需要國際文宣都已經自動搬上國際舞台 另類型抗爭 同時口罩亦可以比你寫上你想寫既野 記者鏡頭會捕捉一切<br />\n<br />\n如果你話擔心帶口罩被捕從而被上門搜查證據 咁你就係自私 因為你既自私從而害死響應既手足 因為你冇帶 狗同藍絲更容易搵到目標 調返轉黎講 全民帶罩同時亦係互相保護大家 免受便衣狗既跟蹤<br />\n<br />\n行動勝於一切口舌之爭<br />\n如果連帶口罩都咁難有共識既 <br />\n呢場運動結局注定完結<br />\n唯有期待下一場真。社會運動<br />\n<br />\n希望連登仔女反省下點解咁呢個po咁多正評<br />\n唔好再見到正評多就幫手㩒多下 睇下內文<br />\n要用腦諗阿各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外<br />\n國際文宣戰線同帶口罩係冇衝突 <br />\n兩樣可以同時做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">Fight for freedom <br />\nStand with Hong Kong</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:<br />\n日日帶 外科嗰隻 焗到仆街 帶到宜家 乜事都冇<br />\n不過日日都受到冇帶罩既香港市民既奇異目光"},{"pid":"0df3709de2a631a92b47787b4d3f5948efbce716","tid":1645103,"uid":15226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:44:14.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27eff5ae299269f94f876a813686d77c13056cc","tid":1645103,"uid":15226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T18:44:31.000Z","msg":"幫手推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c76336fa4374c6f93af036b78da2dca4c7407a29","tid":1645103,"uid":15226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:06:25.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ee5d696ae8d8e3df3e748e1af59bf76dad5e4b71","tid":1645103,"uid":15226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:06:39.000Z","msg":"Push (4/10)"},{"pid":"9783a3a3e6927312752cb863a2140424e8170df2","tid":1645103,"uid":15226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:07:49.000Z","msg":"雖然今日有大量breaking news<br />\n但都係希望大家討論個共識出黎"},{"pid":"35825c490c89e60ad9123016fb2305ad04cb06a8","tid":1645103,"uid":15226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:09:37.000Z","msg":"沖埋涼出黎再推"},{"pid":"345d2f02e0bb3fc197d09b61ad683777757e51f8","tid":1645103,"uid":37058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:17:05.000Z","msg":"算撚數啦巴打 你睇下個po入面既人幾垃圾就知無得救 我有做依樣有做嗰樣點解唔戴口罩就唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e43eed34de3aef98ac6399ce2d6ebb780cffd249","tid":1645103,"uid":94585,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:20:07.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n利申日日戴"},{"pid":"42a1048b43d92ef94e6f96eed39e9147cdbdc6f2","tid":1645103,"uid":76314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:21:59.000Z","msg":"照戴，但夜晚人少個陣自己要小心，尤其女人"},{"pid":"df73a2abbc89ffc4cbf996ed075f62d6cb677e29","tid":1645103,"uid":15226,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"42a1048b43d92ef94e6f96eed39e9147cdbdc6f2","tid":1645103,"uid":76314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:21:59.000Z","msg":"照戴，但夜晚人少個陣自己要小心，尤其女人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:45:36.000Z","msg":"呢個真 夜歸女手足最好帶定防狼工具自衛<br />\n咩工具就自行決定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a57607df50593ca912ef88c29556176f436e5cfe","tid":1645103,"uid":15226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"345d2f02e0bb3fc197d09b61ad683777757e51f8","tid":1645103,"uid":37058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:17:05.000Z","msg":"算撚數啦巴打 你睇下個po入面既人幾垃圾就知無得救 我有做依樣有做嗰樣點解唔戴口罩就唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:45:58.000Z","msg":"比啲信念 we connect！！！"},{"pid":"dc00a892de37bfc1af3e75ffc4a13b24ca3c7771","tid":1645103,"uid":15226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e43eed34de3aef98ac6399ce2d6ebb780cffd249","tid":1645103,"uid":94585,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:20:07.000Z","msg":"支持<br />\n利申日日戴"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:49:49.000Z","msg":"以我所見唔帶罩既手足其實中上年齡比較後生多小小<br />\n所以需要既都係文宣 傳意 <br />\n吸引更多同路人支持"},{"pid":"8912b33353b8209dbedc7b7500a33ca2190240c1","tid":1645103,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:52:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fbf7dc04c31a57e7ae62109050e2437a92076c29","tid":1645103,"uid":80162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T20:00:19.000Z","msg":"仲有個好重要原因 就係可以保護手足！<br />\n<br />\n平時遊行集會 手足都可能會戴住口罩出入<br />\n如果得佢地戴口罩就好易引人注目<br />\n相反，如果全民都有口罩<br />\n手足就可以隨時戴住口罩進場離場 安全好多"},{"pid":"7ea48a9434cfad3ebec3c223c05c16c3c5f26432","tid":1645103,"uid":15754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T20:15:58.000Z","msg":"全民口罩 推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b5617d7ca815dfc535d7bf13e7594641aea6957","tid":1645103,"uid":60936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:11:44.000Z","msg":"我帶日本嗰隻黑口罩好多人望，但嗰隻真係透氣好多。診所外科口罩就冇咁多人望"},{"pid":"d80180e49df38a8248149525a96fd9b7af2fd792","tid":1645103,"uid":153035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:13:44.000Z","msg":"支持日日戴，夜返一條友驚popo逗既咪除lo,至少安全既時候都要戴掛"},{"pid":"0237d219444f05fe0c8384188453b9f136dcf940","tid":1645103,"uid":91230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"345d2f02e0bb3fc197d09b61ad683777757e51f8","tid":1645103,"uid":37058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:17:05.000Z","msg":"算撚數啦巴打 你睇下個po入面既人幾垃圾就知無得救 我有做依樣有做嗰樣點解唔戴口罩就唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:22:59.000Z","msg":"咁低成本嘅表態都唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67a5eb367a1888e4d707eb4d171e92de78cc7b12","tid":1645103,"uid":91230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"345d2f02e0bb3fc197d09b61ad683777757e51f8","tid":1645103,"uid":37058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:17:05.000Z","msg":"算撚數啦巴打 你睇下個po入面既人幾垃圾就知無得救 我有做依樣有做嗰樣點解唔戴口罩就唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:23:23.000Z","msg":"仲要搵藉口呢樣嗰樣<br />\n唉"},{"pid":"59062a78a635699b8110d9a2474a65b4541feb47","tid":1645103,"uid":91230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b5617d7ca815dfc535d7bf13e7594641aea6957","tid":1645103,"uid":60936,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:11:44.000Z","msg":"我帶日本嗰隻黑口罩好多人望，但嗰隻真係透氣好多。診所外科口罩就冇咁多人望"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:24:43.000Z","msg":"外科嗰隻啱驚俾人篤灰嗰啲<br />\n俾人望就咳兩聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3342301fb04f893021eea908272417f57969eeec","tid":1645103,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:24:58.000Z","msg":"點解又要因為口罩比位人入"},{"pid":"5443f84eced1908e9642517388fba870f21820f3","tid":1645103,"uid":83819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:27:56.000Z","msg":"我自己親身體驗<br />\n<br />\n帶口罩唔係太方便<br />\n我多數番工同放工帶<br />\n中午食飯無帶<br />\n<br />\n但我中午個陣搵左取代品<br />\n就係全黑帽（大約40蚊）<br />\n<br />\n所以大家係無口罩下<br />\n<br />\n可以全民帶黑帽"},{"pid":"52fcf7751b92d9a586d3ef22f612a1fdce3e74a8","tid":1645103,"uid":173936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:30:19.000Z","msg":"鼻敏感患者表示完全冇問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4acd97667e73fbad9004e70df0d99d588ed4ae1b","tid":1645103,"uid":232540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:31:59.000Z","msg":"戴個口罩真係咁難？我都仲日日戴緊<br />\n怕乜野？"}]}